{"tid":2243734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【要有一套】同樣宣稱「薄」　30款安全套之間平均厚度可差逾四倍","createTime":"2020-10-15T03:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T03:36:14.000Z","uid":227971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7578e051656100656413c423829f0138e04d7776","tid":2243734,"uid":227971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:14:18.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】消委會測試30款安全套，發現同樣以「薄」為宣傳重點的安全套厚度可相差逾4倍。<br />\n<br />\n消委會參考國際標準量度方法，測試每款安全套13個樣本，每個樣本量度三個特定位置，再計算平均值；發現6款原料為合成物料聚氨酯的安全套較薄，平均厚度為0.019毫米至0.030毫米；22款橡膠安全套的厚度差異最大，平均厚度是0.039毫米至0.093毫米，反映不同物料之間，最薄和最厚樣本厚度可相差逾四倍。<br />\n<br />\n消委會又發現，不是每款安全套都有列出量度的單位，例如有兩款就在包裝列出「001」這組數字，但量得的厚度分別是0.054及0.055毫米。代理商回覆時指，從未聲稱過「001」與產品厚度有關。有部分安全套則產品說明不足，沒有中文說明或使用期限等。<br />\n<br />\n消委會提醒選購安全套時，最實際方法是先買少量試用，親自感受舒適度；亦要留意安全套在零售點的陳列位置，以免買入可能因為高溫或光而加快老化產品；選購後，亦應存放於室內陰涼地方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=409109\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D409109&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyif3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=18a4aea7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D409109&h=3e8d5c2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=409109</a>"},{"pid":"458d7f1060f8435878efb33f11bfcc396f4dd3a1","tid":2243734,"uid":39064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:29:59.000Z","msg":"001只係個名 唔係厚度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89a16cb078c0a7a25fc5dbd647a96b4fba6ddb7","tid":2243734,"uid":6316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:32:01.000Z","msg":"連登冇人用dom"},{"pid":"0c52dcc245479a2f95e163fcdcbdfd6ec2ed847f","tid":2243734,"uid":227971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b89a16cb078c0a7a25fc5dbd647a96b4fba6ddb7","tid":2243734,"uid":6316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:32:01.000Z","msg":"連登冇人用dom"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:34:06.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"c24fa73f54458bf5b6d9fbb33be8ae5ed61bfc6b","tid":2243734,"uid":227971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T03:36:14.000Z","msg":"想知道0.019mm係邊個牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}